{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839800315,"sessionID":"ses_287b378c1ffe854YLU3MLuwv1Z","part":{"id":"prt_d784ce6bc001xmQ33gtUjkFZ1M","messageID":"msg_d784cd1bc001600N9S3tmqCTNy","sessionID":"ses_287b378c1ffe854YLU3MLuwv1Z","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2403c1ae62d24d12aa0eec64","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/` directory structure\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/register.go` - register API group\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## Phase 2: Type Definitions\n20: \n21: - [ ] **2.1** Define `CodeInterpreterPhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\n22: - [ ] **2.2** Define `CodeInterpreterCondition` struct (type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime)\n23: - [ ] **2.3** Define `KernelSpec` struct (language, image, resources)\n24: - [ ] **2.4** Define `SessionConfig` struct (timeout, idleTimeout, maxSessions)\n25: - [ ] **2.5** Define `SecurityPolicy` struct (allowedPackages, blockedOperations, networkAccess)\n26: - [ ] **2.6** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct (kernel, session, security, resources)\n27: - [ ] **2.7** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct (phase, conditions, activeSessions, startTime, lastTransitionTime)\n28: - [ ] **2.8** Define `CodeInterpreter` struct (TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, Status)\n29: - [ ] **2.9** Define `CodeInterpreterList` struct (TypeMeta, ListMeta, Items)\n30: - [ ] **2.10** Add JSON tags (camelCase) and protobuf tags to all types\n31: - [ ] **2.11** Implement `runtime.Object` interface for CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## Phase 3: Defaults & Validation\n36: \n37: - [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/defaults.go`\n38: - [ ] **3.2** Implement `SetDefaults_CodeInterpreter` - set default phase to Pending, default kernel settings\n39: - [ ] **3.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/validation.go`\n40: - [ ] **3.4** Implement `ValidateCodeInterpreter` - validate spec fields (kernel language, resource values, security policies)\n41: - [ ] **3.5** Implement `ValidateCodeInterpreterStatusUpdate` - validate status transitions and field immutability\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## Phase 4: CRD Manifest Generation\n46: \n47: - [ ] **4.1** Add `+genclient` and `+k8s:deepcopy-gen` markers to type definitions\n48: - [ ] **4.2** Add `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` and `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` markers\n49: - [ ] **4.3** Add `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` markers for kubectl output (NAME, PHASE, KERNEL, AGE)\n50: - [ ] **4.4** Run `make gen-crd` (controller-gen) to generate CRD YAML\n51: - [ ] **4.5** Verify generated manifest at `manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n52: - [ ] **4.6** Validate OpenAPI v3 schema in generated CRD\n53: \n54: ---\n55: \n56: ## Phase 5: Client Code Generation\n57: \n58: - [ ] **5.1** Update `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` if needed\n59: - [ ] **5.2** Update `hack/update-codegen.sh` with API group info\n60: - [ ] **5.3** Run `make gen-client` to generate clientset, listers, informers\n61: - [ ] **5.4** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/clientset/versioned/`\n62: - [ ] **5.5** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/listers/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/`\n63: - [ ] **5.6** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/informers/externalversions/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/`\n64: \n65: ---\n66: \n67: ## Phase 6: Unit Tests\n68: \n69: - [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n70: - [ ] **6.2** Test type round-trip serialization (Go → JSON → Go)\n71: - [ ] **6.3** Test `SetDefaults_CodeInterpreter` behavior\n72: - [ ] **6.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/validation_test.go`\n73: - [ ] **6.5** Test valid CodeInterpreter specs pass validation\n74: - [ ] **6.6** Test invalid specs fail validation (unsupported languages, negative resources)\n75: - [ ] **6.7** Test status update validation (phase transitions, immutable fields)\n76: - [ ] **6.8** Test `AddToScheme` registration works correctly\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Phase 7: Integration & Verification\n81: \n82: - [ ] **7.1** Run `make test` - all unit tests pass\n83: - [ ] **7.2** Run `make verify` - code generation is up to date\n84: - [ ] **7.3** Apply CRD to test cluster: `kubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n85: - [ ] **7.4** Verify `kubectl get codeinterpreter` shows custom columns\n86: - [ ] **7.5** Create sample CodeInterpreter YAML in `examples/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n87: - [ ] **7.6** Apply sample and verify resource is created\n88: - [ ] **7.7** Verify Go client can create/get/update CodeInterpreter resources\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## Verification Checklist\n93: \n94: - [ ] All Go code compiles without errors\n95: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/...` passes with ≥80% coverage\n96: - [ ] CRD manifest validates with `kubeval` or `kubectl --dry-run=server`\n97: - [ ] Generated client code is up to date (`git diff` shows no changes after `make gen-client`)\n98: - [ ] Example YAML applies successfully to test cluster\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## Dependencies\n103: \n104: | Task | Depends On |\n105: |------|------------|\n106: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n107: | Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n108: | Phase 4 | Phase 2 |\n109: | Phase 5 | Phase 4 |\n110: | Phase 6 | Phase 2, 3 |\n111: | Phase 7 | Phase 4, 5, 6 |\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## References\n116: \n117: - Proposal: `changes/AR-002/proposal.md`\n118: - Implementation Plan: `proposal.md#implementation-plan`\n119: - Success Criteria: `proposal.md#success-criteria`\n120: - API Conventions: `https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md`\n121: - Related: `changes/AR-001/` (AgentRuntime CRD)\n\n(End of file - total 121 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/` directory structure\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/register.go` - register API group\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Type Definitions\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775839800306,"end":1775839800313}}}}
